Andrew Chan and Myruan Sukumaran will be executed at midnight on Tuesday . 
  The pair will be given white clothing to wear and a choice of whether to be blindfolded . 
  They will face a firing squad of 12 riflemen in the jungle on Nusakambangan Island in Java . 
  Three of the riflemen will have live rounds and the men will be shot in the heart . 
  Millions of viewers watched a chilling reenactment of the execution on Indonesian TV in January . 
  The Bali Nine ringleaders will be led to the firing squad at the stroke of midnight . 
  The men will face 12 marksmen with only three of them holding loaded guns at the stoke of midnight  . 
 